{"tid":1707014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 求你地升級一下先","createTime":"2019-11-11T08:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T08:56:15.000Z","uid":164152,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5877c5be3aadfbb1cb3b4370328ef163fe6ba5a2","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:14:23.000Z","msg":"升級一下自己嘅武力<br />\n起碼都拎啲武器旁身<br />\n棍、鐵通、刀，咩都好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好赤手空拳</strong></span></span><br />\n我唔係話要迫你拎武器硬碰硬<br />\n而係有武器揸手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有威嚇作用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你哋見到次次出嚟<br />\n知你地乜春都冇<br />\n咪夠薑揸車撞你<br />\n咪夠膽抆槍射你<br />\n你乜都冇仲夠膽上前反抗咩<br />\n<br />\n一個人拎武器可能分別唔大<br />\n你成班人都揸住碌嘢就一定唔敢亂嚟<br />\n拎武器係手真係基本嘢<br />\n而點樣利用把武器就自己揸主意<br />\n拎黎進攻？用嚟救人？定阻嚇藍屍黑警？<br />\n自己話事冇人迫你<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n唔好再比<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「法律」「道德」</strong></span></span>綁死自己<br />\n又話呢樣唔啱嗰樣唔啱<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n諗下對家點解次次都贏<br />\n因為人地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>凌駕法律</strong></span></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>冇道德可言</strong></span></span><br />\n再唔升級一下<br />\n呢個困局會持續落去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327f1673fe438c605336dce04da3f8788ff7b76d","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"有任何意見都講兩句"},{"pid":"8f4d33c260a64c4542aa17ea7361631679532ac3","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"自推 1/50"},{"pid":"2bae33a2dfbc50066b95d446ce0ae36b9b46158d","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"2/50"},{"pid":"0c37b4d16e2a5e054fd00c729539e2cd511b93a7","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"3/50"},{"pid":"9ec8d046de8aff18f2350dbca0c237b2867f9c01","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"4/50"},{"pid":"22f18157dc991c5a85e0aa588c799cb9bfd09773","tid":1707014,"uid":263038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n正路你要攞住老牛加威脅佢生命安全先可以舉槍警示<br />\n但而家你赤手空拳都照射<br />\n不如真係攞老牛"},{"pid":"3838cd49ced188b5a8d618ebd3cc57f0dff846b2","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"5/50"},{"pid":"c4c27e9aea438b522b154b6c02674108a3cce473","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:18:47.000Z","msg":"6/50"},{"pid":"d32934735e4df2586c16aa1fa99f4a6334114112","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22f18157dc991c5a85e0aa588c799cb9bfd09773","tid":1707014,"uid":263038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n正路你要攞住老牛加威脅佢生命安全先可以舉槍警示<br />\n但而家你赤手空拳都照射<br />\n不如真係攞老牛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n你拎住啲嘢行行企企<br />\n都好過乜嘢都冇"},{"pid":"6c84b0169bd8f9f1497fb2a16d77b029ae9a1585","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:22:53.000Z","msg":"我預咗傳媒/藍屍/五毛會就呢點煽風點火<br />\n話示威者好危險乜乜柒柒<br />\n如果比人屌可以保障手足安全<br />\n就比佢哋慢慢屌"},{"pid":"c2d22e95817c45c03eaa528a05e9d0540fd19872","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:23:12.000Z","msg":"7/50"},{"pid":"251a42a3036c895980a55d2b936cccdf16d678fb","tid":1707014,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:24:02.000Z","msg":"揸車撞啦屌"},