":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n我做過咩洗唔洗開個list出嚟交代？<br />\n<br />\n你唔撚係覺得呢個程度就夠？<br />\n<br />\n我知有人升緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但好撚多人都仲係乜撚都冇我先開po求你地</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母柒頭皮"},{"pid":"f7cf46d0ca22702cde1db7077355ce0cbeac368b","tid":1707014,"uid":164152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4992fdeaf1c598147536a49f538d672acee0e39d","tid":1707014,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:30:29.000Z","msg":"今日已經升級得好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"但仲有好多進步空間 手足要再加油"}]}